PRUEBAMASTER
Steps for development
======================

1. Create the project for iOS/Android

1.1. iOS Project

 A) To create the iOS Project, download and install the latest Phonegap into XCode.
 B) Download the project from here: https://www.dropbox.com/s/s7spvn734i8havk/Tocarta%20iOS.zip
 C) Import the project and fix bad references 

1.2. Android Project

 A) To create the Android Project, download and install the latest Phonegap and Android.
 B) Download the project from here: https://www.dropbox.com/s/hhkau08mq19yb89/TocartaAndroid.zip
 C) Import the project (from Eclipse do: new android project from existing sources) and fix bad references

3. When styling or theming

./public/www/styles/compass watch

check this for docs: http://www.slideshare.net/senchainc/theming-sencha-touch


Steps for production
======================

1. Compile Stylesheets

./public/www/styles/compass compile

2. Setup the config environment: config.js

3. Run jsb3 script (to compress and deploy js and css)

$> sencha create jsb -a index.html -p tc.jsb3
$> sencha build -p tc.jsb3 -d ../deploy/tocarta/1_6_4 -v

